  "nameCn": "质粒小提 (碱裂解法)",
  "notes": {
    "en": "Dilute to 1× before use. Classic alkaline lysis method. Yields 5–20 µg from 3 mL overnight culture. A260/280 should be 1.8–2.0 for pure DNA.",
